<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v1" title="Q30_v1" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En ciertos mapas planos se cumple la siguiente regla: el número de regiones (R) más el número de vértices (V) es igual al número de fronteras (F) más 2, es decir, <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>F</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
    <p>En un mapa que cumple esta regla, se observan 9 vértices y 20 fronteras. ¿Cuántas regiones tiene el mapa?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">11<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>F</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la regla exige <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>. Si <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>11</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, pero <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>. Por eso 11 no satisface la regla.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">13<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Con <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>F</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, la regla queda <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>, resulta <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>. Restando 9 a ambos lados, <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">27<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:math>. Pero el otro lado de la regla es <m:math><m:mi>F</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>, 27 no cumple la regla.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">31<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>31</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>31</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:math>. Sin embargo, <m:math><m:mi>F</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math>, 31 no satisface la condición del enunciado.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la regla del mapa</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado dice que en estos mapas se cumple:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>F</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar los datos conocidos</strong></p>
            <p>Se observan 9 vértices y 20 fronteras, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Simplificar el lado derecho</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar el número de regiones</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos 9 a ambos lados de la igualdad:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>13</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El mapa tiene <strong>13 regiones</strong>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>